# Builder OS

Builder OS is a macOS AI Product Development Operating System built with Tauri v2, React, TypeScript, Tailwind, shadcn/ui, and SQLite.

## Architecture

- Tauri Rust layer owns secrets, DB, shell commands, external API calls
- React renderer never holds API keys
- Product Brain is the single source of truth
- All external actions require user approval

## Conventions

- Feature-based folder structure under `src/features/`
- Zustand for state management
- Tauri commands via `src/lib/tauri-commands.ts`
- shadcn/ui components in `src/components/ui/`
